title: Leisha’s 7-Hour Sobriety

description:
PANTS with Kate Moennig and Leisha Hailey

Produced by Melisa D. Monts and Diamond MPrint Productions

Edited by Diane Kang 

 

Leisha attends a party as a guest event photographer. Kate discovers grass is real. They then explain how they became friends with a soccer team owner. Talk about scoring.
